                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Relationships</h3><p class="indent">John and
                                Severus of
                                Antioch had a professional relationship. <a href="/3085-21" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent">Severus of Antioch
                            sent a letter to John. <a href="/3085-22" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent">
                            John and Anonymous 3777 
                            were married.
                         <a href="/3037-3" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Events</h3><p class="indent">
                            Severus replied to a letter of 
                            John 
                            on the subject of not communing with heretics.
                            
                                
                            
                         <a href="/3037-1" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent">
                            Anonymous 3778 wrote a letter to 
                            John 
                            disclosing false theology.
                         <a href="/3037-11" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent">
                            John wrote a letter to 
                            Severus
                            commending his wife to Severus and 
                            discussing his refusal to commune with heretics.
                            
                                
                            
